# 🌿 InkandIvy

InkandIvy is a modern Pinterest-inspired web application designed to help users discover and organize aesthetic inspiration across categories like home décor, fashion, DIY, lifestyle, productivity, and more.

## ✨ Features

- Responsive Pinterest-style masonry grid
- Modern and minimal UI
- Dark & Light mode
- Search and category filtering
- Smooth animations with Framer Motion
- Infinite scrolling
- Lazy image loading
- Mobile-first responsive design
- SEO-friendly
- Optimized for Vercel deployment

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- React (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion
- React Router
- Lucide React
- JavaScript (ES6+)

