## 🚀 Getting Started

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Kaviya-41/inkandivy.git
```

Navigate to the project:

```bash
cd inkandivy
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Start the development server:

```bash
npm run dev
```

## 🎨 Design Inspiration

Inspired by Pinterest, Apple, and modern editorial design with a focus on clean layouts, smooth animations, and an elegant user experience.

